<subSubSection pageId="68" pageNumber="463" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="68.[118,1325,883,2178]" pageId="68" pageNumber="463">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[118,353,1711,1744]" pageId="68" pageNumber="463">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Nilgiri Highland Shrews are said to be crepuscular but might be active intermittently night and day.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
